If docker compose is used.
Pack the content of "server stuff" and export.py in one place and execute “docker compose up --build” in the terminal. 

Create and start 3 Docker containers:
dwd-exporter to see all the data you get
prometheus-1 for Prometheus server
grafana-1 for Grafana

Ports:
dwd-exporter: 9110:9110 (http://localhost:9110/metrics)
Prometheus: 9090:9090   (http://localhost:9090/query)
Grafana: 3000:3000 
open docker-compose.yml to change ports or start less containers

Flask needed for Phyton file
based on Pyton 3.12. change dockerfile if your version is different

schanzer is the main Charackter 
